lines.text: Brother pussycats! We've been skidded out, scooted out, backed out and booted out! But tonight, we was scared out! It's unhospitabitatble, and furthermore, it's un-cat-stitutional!
[the cats have thrown Porky into the snow]
Pardon me, but d-d-does anyone in the audience kn-know somebody who kn-knows somebody that has a house to rent?
Are we men, or are we mice?

[as he smacks the tiny cat]
Smack!
Aha! I think I've got it.
